<tr><td class="smtitle" id="9">Items search</td></tr>
<tr><td>
<div>For registered and not registered users search is available from the main page. On the main page one can search by a key word\phase and in categories.</div>
<div>Using advanced search you can search:
<br>- by the lot number 
<br>- by the user's ID 
<br>- by the key word if necessary using the category and location filter.
</div>
</td></tr>
